yName":"日菜","body":"居然－，為什麼？　這樣沒辦法讓人產生動力嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"雖然是會很有動力……\n但那樣的話，不就會變成大家都是為了獎品才打掃嗎","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"那也行吧。不行嗎－？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"校園整潔日啊，\n本來是希望同學們能更著重環境整潔才舉辦的活動喔？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"要是準備了獎品，\n就會變成只限那天大家一頭熱過後就結束了……\n我覺得無法讓大家更注重相關議題，這樣不太好","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"嗯－，是這樣嗎－？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"而且啊，自己動手來打掃自己周遭環境，\n不是會讓人對校園更有感情嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"？　為什麼自己動手打掃過後，就會對那個地方產生感情啊？\n這兩件事情無關吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"呃？　該怎麼說呢，就是……\n有多認真打掃，就會產生相對應的好感……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"嗯－？　好吧－算了。\n總之小六花的廣播表現得很好，\n所以也沒有必要辦大賽了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"話說回來，為什麼他的表現會突然好轉呢？\n真的突然間有一百八十度的轉變對吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"的確是這樣沒錯。應該是有什麼祕訣吧……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"嗨，兩位。能打擾你們一會嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"啊，是薰薰耶－！　快進來快進來！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"抱歉在你們忙碌時來打擾。我來提交\n這次話劇社定期公演必要的相關文件……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"好的！　我收下了。\n我會在今天內確認完畢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"啊啊，麻煩你們了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"啊，我說啊－薰薰你知道嗎？\n小六花的校內廣播，不是突然間變好了嗎？\n你覺得那是為什麼啊？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"哎呀，看來小六花\n也獲得學生會長的肯定了呢……那我就心安了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"所以，意思是，薰薰有幫忙？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"咦？　是這樣嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"在不久之前，\n我和麻彌的確有對他進行了演技的指導","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"不過，我真的也只是提供了些許的幫助而已。\n剩下的都是小六花透過自身努力獲得的結果","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"原來是這樣！\n如果有薰薰和小彌的協助，就說得通了－","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"因為緊張而顫抖不已的小六花，靠著自己的力量\n發掘出了全新的自我……啊啊，真是太虛幻了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"嗯－。新的自己嗎－。\n校內廣播有那麼嚴重嗎？\n我不是很理解耶－","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"把想到的事情嘶啪啪地說出來，基本上就能炒熱氣氛了吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"我，我覺得那應該只有日菜學姊才做得到……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"呵呵，想必日菜不用多經琢磨，\n就能帶來非常有趣的廣播吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev162-ep5-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"不過俗話說「十人十色，百人百樣」\n日菜有日菜的虛幻